# CMHG file format syntax colouring

syntax "CMHG" "(^|/)cmhg/[^/]+$"
comment "; "

## Preprocessor
color yellow "^# *(define|include|ifn?def|endif|elif|else|if)"

## Declarations
color cyan "^[a-z\-]*: *.*$"
color white "^[a-z\-]*:"
color magenta "^[a-z\-]*"

## Numbers
color yellow "&[0-9A-Fa-f]+"

## Comments
color green   ";.*"
